Depends: ${misc:Depends}, php-vitexsoftware-multiflexi-core (>= 2.9), php-vgrem-php-spo, multiflexi-cli (>= 2.2.0)
Description: MultiFlexi Microsoft 365 credential prototype
 Office 365 / SharePoint credential prototype for MultiFlexi core.
 Provides the CredentialProtoType class defining tenant, site, client
 id/secret and user credential fields, plus a two-phase SharePoint
 availability check built on the php-spo library.

